trans-unit.source: Provides an external process for running add-ins out-of-process from the host application.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en extern process för att köra tillägg out-of-process från värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: To activate an add-in in an external process, pass an AddInProcess object to the appropriate <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName> method overload.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill aktivera ett tillägg i en extern process, skicka ett AddInProcess-objekt till lämplig <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName>metodöverlagringen.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The executable that runs the add-in is obtained from one of two files installed with the .NET Framework under the Windows directory.
trans-unit.target: Den körbara filen som kör tillägget hämtas från en av två filer som installeras med .NET Framework Windows-katalogen.

trans-unit.source: By default, the executable that matches the bits-per-word of the host application is used.
trans-unit.target: Som standard används den körbara filen som matchar det bitar per ordet i värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: If the host is a 64-bit process, AddInProcess.exe is run; otherwise, AddInProcess32.exe is run.
trans-unit.target: Om värden har en 64-bitars process, körs AddInProcess.exe; Annars körs AddInProcess32.exe.

trans-unit.source: To specify the way the executable is selected, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29> constructor to create the AddInProcess object.
trans-unit.target: Ange hur den körbara filen är markerad i <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>konstruktorn för att skapa objektet AddInProcess.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This constructor has the same effect as using the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29> constructor with the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName> flag, to specify that the process that runs the add-in will have the same bits-per-word as the host process.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn har samma effekt som använder den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>konstruktor med den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName>Flagga för att ange att den process som körs i tillägget har samma bits-per-ord som värdprocessen.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> class, specifying the bits-per-word of the process in which the add-in runs.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> klassen som anger det bitar per ordet i processen där tillägget körs.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows how `platform` affects the bits-per-word of the process on different operating systems: ||32-bit operating system|64-bit operating system| |-|------------------------------|------------------------------| |Host|32-bit|Same as the host process| |AnyCPU|32-bit|64-bit| |X86|32-bit|32-bit| |X64|Exception is thrown|64-bit|
trans-unit.target: I följande tabell visas hur `platform` påverkar den bitar per word av processen på olika operativsystem:.&32;-bitars operativsystem |&64;-bitars operativsystem | |-|------------------------------|------------------------------| | Värden |&32;-bitars | Samma som värdprocessen | | AnyCPU |&32;-bitars |&64;-bitars | | X86 |&32;-bitars |&32;-bitars | | X64 | Undantag |&64;-bitars |

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies the bits-per-word of the process that runs the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Ett värde som anger den bitar per word av den process som körs i tillägget.

trans-unit.source: The registry entry for the path to the executable (AddInProcess.exe or AddInProcess32.exe) is missing.
trans-unit.target: Registerposten för sökvägen till den körbara filen (AddInProcess.exe eller AddInProcess32.exe) saknas.

trans-unit.source: -or- The executable is missing.
trans-unit.target: - eller - den körbara filen saknas.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> object represents the host application process.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om aktuellt <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> -objektet representerar värdprocess för programmet.

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is `true`, the add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Om värdet för den här egenskapen är `true`, är det tillägg som körs i processen med värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: In that case, using the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A> method throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: I så fall använder <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A>eller <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A>metoden genererar <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property returns an <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> object that represents the host application process if the add-in is running in-process.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen returnerar ett <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>objekt som representerar värdprocess för programmet om det tillägg som körs i processen.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> object corresponds to the current process; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> objekt motsvarar aktuellt processen, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether to keep the external process alive.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om keep alive för extern process.

trans-unit.source: Set this property to `false` to aggressively shut down the external process after the last add-in inside the process has been shut down.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen `false` aggressivt stänga extern process efter det senaste tillägget i processen har avslutats.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the external process should be kept alive; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om extern process bör hållas aktiva; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the bits-per-word of the process in which the out-of-process add-in is run.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar det bitar per ordet i processen där tillägget utanför processen körs.

trans-unit.source: The bits-per-word is set when the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> object is initialized, and cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: Bitar per word anges när den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>objektet har initierats och kan inte ändras.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>

trans-unit.source: The bits-per-word of the process that runs the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Bits-per-ordet av den process som körs i tillägget.

trans-unit.source: Gets the process ID of the external process.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar process-ID för extern process.

trans-unit.source: Use this property for debugging.
trans-unit.target: Använd den här egenskapen för felsökning.

trans-unit.source: The process ID, or -1 if the external process has not started.
trans-unit.target: Process-ID eller -1 om extern process inte har startats.

trans-unit.source: Forcibly shuts down the external process.
trans-unit.target: Framtvingar stängs av extern process.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the external process was running and is successfully shut down; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if there is no active process associated with the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om extern process kördes och har stängts. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om det är inte aktiv process som är associerad med den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Tillägget är körs i processen med värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Starting and stopping the process is allowed only for external processes, not for the host process.
trans-unit.target: Starta och stoppa processen tillåts endast för externa processer, inte för värdprocessen.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the process represented by the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> object is about to be shut down.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar när processen som representeras av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> objektet håller på att stängas av.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Starts the external process.
trans-unit.target: Startar extern process.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om processen startade; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om processen körs redan.

trans-unit.source: The add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Tillägget är körs i processen med värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Starting and stopping the process is allowed only for external processes, not for the host process.
trans-unit.target: Starta och stoppa processen tillåts endast för externa processer, inte för värdprocessen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of seconds to allow for the process to start.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger antalet sekunder att starta processen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 10 seconds.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är 10 sekunder.

trans-unit.source: This property is usually used during debugging, to increase the startup time for the process that runs the out-of-process add-in.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen används vanligtvis vid felsökning, öka starttiden för den process som kör out-of-process-tillägg.

trans-unit.source: The number of seconds to allow for process startup.
trans-unit.target: Antal sekunder så att processen startades.

trans-unit.target: Processen körs redan.

trans-unit.target: Det tilldelade värdet är mindre än 0 (noll).
